1. Idemo u *pravcu* Beograda. (We are going in the direction of Belgrade.)
2. Koji *pravac* treba da izaberemo? (Which direction should we choose?)
3. Želim da se usmerim ka drugom *pravcu*. (I want to direct myself towards a different direction.)
4. Ona je *pravac* promenila nakon razgovora sa šefom. (She changed direction after the conversation with the boss.)
5. Ovaj voz ide u suprotnom *pravcu* od željene destinacije. (This train is going in the opposite direction from the desired destination.)
6. Imate li neki *pravac* za rešavanje ovog problema? (Do you have any direction for solving this problem?)
7. U ovoj školi se možete školovati u *pravcu* medicinske sestre. (In this school, you can study to become a nurse.)
8. Moramo biti sigurni da idemo u *pravom pravcu*. (We need to be sure that we are going in the right direction.)
9. Kada stigneš u gradski centar, *pravac* autobuske stanice je levo. (When you arrive at the city center, the direction of the bus station is to the left.)
10. *Pravac* naše kompanije je inovacija. (The direction of our company is innovation.)